(2, '2020-01-15', 1, 'Lost Bob Ross Transcript Found!', 'It doesn\'t take much, but you have to devote that time. That\'s a fantastic little cloud. Fun time! Quiet, quiet little bushes. Maybe this is the same cloud. You want to be able to control these rascals. We\'re looking for a nice, even distribution of color. You know what? Let\'s get crazy.\r\n\r\nCreate that little fuzzy look. There\'s too many complicated things in our life already. It\'ll open whole new worlds for you once you learn to make friends with this knife. You wouldn\'t buy somebody else\'s mistakes; nobody\'s going to buy yours. Get nervous. He\'s got the leanies! Clouds could very well be the freest things in nature. Just let them fall right out of your brush.\r\n\r\nAnyone can paint! Learn to work with anything that happens. Just mix it up real good. Let\'s play some games! You can begin making all kinds of beautiful shapes up in the sky. Very, very... let me say that one more time: very. We\'ll make those decisions later. We\'ll let our imaginations take us wherever we want to go today.\r\n\r\nYou decide -- you have to make these big decisions. We\'re gonna play some games here with different planes. Don\'t piddle with them -- don\'t worry about them. We are really trying to teach you a technique. We\'re not trying to teach you to copy. The just do nice things for you. We become mud-mixers. Do you want to get crazy? Don\'t let your trees get too symmetrical... too even.', '<a id=\'Z74zONwDRGVyeEsEuWDxsw\' class=\'gie-single\' href=\'http://www.gettyimages.com/detail/996292232\' target=\'_blank\' style=\'color:#a7a7a7;text-decoration:none;font-weight:normal !important;border:none;display:inline-block;\'>Embed from Getty Images</a><script>window.gie=window.gie||function(c){(gie.q=gie.q||[]).push(c)};gie(function(){gie.widgets.load({id:\'Z74zONwDRGVyeEsEuWDxsw\',sig:\'NqUF5rjLE-L0qW66wbY2jdZVdexWumjY0dhYvUtPnxI=\',w:\'594px\',h:\'396px\',items:\'996292232\',caption: false ,tld:\'com\',is360: fals